@EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5058

### Analyze a document summary
POST {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/analyze/document
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
	"documentText": "Section 4 defines password rotation, MFA enforcement, and quarterly access reviews.",
	"documentName": "Access Control SOP",
	"focusAreas": ["Access Control", "Privileged Accounts"],
	"evidenceTags": ["policy", "sop"]
}

### Compare a document excerpt with a requirement
POST {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/analyze/match
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
	"requirement": "The vendor must encrypt data at rest using AES-256.",
	"documentText": "All customer data is stored on Azure SQL with Transparent Data Encryption enabled.",
	"hints": [
		"Look for explicit encryption mechanisms.",
		"Mention of AES-256 counts as strong evidence."
	]
}

### Fetch gap recommendations
GET {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/analyze/gaps?framework=ISO-27001&focus=Access

### Compliance report
GET {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/report/compliance/1

### Gap report (AI summary included)
GET {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/report/gaps/1

### AI report suggestions
POST {{EvidenceAnalyzer_HostAddress}}/report/suggestions
Content-Type: application/json
